<br>
*this* post by Merloc is completly just, and very smart.   As all the guilds are trying thier hardest to get along (I hope), some people may not be comfortable yet.   No one is blaming anyone on *this* post, if you want to place blame, or defend blame about the &quot;sot missing timelimit&quot; go to the other thread Merloc started.  We all need some nice solid ground rules, so that *no one* not just SoT, but NB, BoTs, TL, and any other guild that enters high end rotations do not break the rules we *all* agree apon.   And hopefully this will help with peace on the server, becuase there will be no misinformation ... everyone will know how much time they have on a rotation, and what happens if its broken.    <br>
<br>
So I ask you all that read this thread, please post only suggestive comments, and leave the flaming to Flame Central?  <br>
<br>
Thank you.<br>
<br>
