<br>
When SoL comes out, there will be more incentive for people to go kill non rotation mobs instead of rotation mobs.  The whole point of this rotation is to prevent inter guild conflict.<br>
<br>
Go read other threads, and you will see that people are already flaming over the fact that some guilds have gone over the 24 hour time limit, and insinuating this is a ploy to destroy the rotations.<br>
<br>
If there are penalties in place, then the system continues to work even when the players don't, and then there is no need to abandon it.<br>
