hr> &quot;From the moment the mob spawns (or you are notified that the prior guild is passing) you have 24 hours to kill that mob or pass to the next guild. After 24 hours the mob automatically passes to the next guild.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I agree .. and don't ... the big problem is what happened with KT the other day .. SoT's 24 hours were up, so what happens if Tindi or Bots went in to rightfully take KT cause the 24 hours are up ... sot was still there .. this would have caused much havoc.    Havoc is what we are trying to prevent.<br>
<br>
Merloc is postiong his ideas on penelties, in no way is he god of the server and saying what he says goes.  He is giving out ideas in hopes everyone agrees on something.   So if you don't agree with Merloc, post your own thoughts ... again, these rotations are to benifit everyone on the rotation.  <br>
<br>
Some people are saying that punishment is wrong .. well okay, but if everyone agrees to a certian 'punishment' then it isn't so bad.     Yes I know its hard to get *everyone* to agree 100% ... but we are all civilized enough people who can come to agreements, I am sure. <p><CENTER>
